1.10	Nilgiri_Press	Eknath Easwaran	From 1960 he gave classes on meditation in the San Francisco Bay Area. He met his wife Christine at one of these talks. Together with his wife, he founded the Blue Mountain Center of Meditation in 1961. After a four-year stay in India, he returned to the Bay Area in 1965	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/0f/Eknath_Easwaran_courtesy_of_the_Blue_Mountain_Center_of_Meditation.jpg/220px-Eknath_Easwaran_courtesy_of_the_Blue_Mountain_Center_of_Meditation.jpg
